OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FCandidates for the Makerfield by-
OL,7,Felection are being announced in a
OL,8,Fpolitical race which could lead to a
OL,9,Fnew prime minister.
OL,11,FLabour and Reform UK have confirmed
OL,12,Fwho will stand for the election -
OL,13,Fwhich is most likely to take place in
OL,14,F18 June - with Greater Manchester
OL,15,FMayor Andy Burnham confirmed as
OL,16,Fstanding.
OL,18,FReform UK has chosen Robert Kenyon, a
OL,19,Flocal plumber who contested the seat
OL,20,Ffor the party in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
