PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FAnnouncing his party's candidate,
OL,7,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage MP
OL,8,Fdescribed the contest as a "David
OL,9,Fversus Goliath battle".
OL,11,FMr Burnham has put himself forward as
OL,12,Fthe candidate to "change Labour",
OL,13,Fusing a campaign video to call for a
OL,14,F"new path for Britain".
OL,16,FIf he returns to Parliament, Mr
OL,17,FBurnham is widely expected to
OL,18,Fchallenge Sir Keir Starmer for the
OL,19,FLabour leadership, but the Prime
OL,20,FMinister has insisted he will not
OL,21,F"walk away" from Downing Street.
