CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FThe by-election was triggered by
OL,7,Fformer minister Josh Simons quitting
OL,8,Fthe Makerfield seat to make way for
OL,9,Fthe Greater Manchester Mayor to run
OL,10,Ffor a return to Westminster and a
OL,11,Fpossible challenge against Sir Keir.
OL,13,FThe news of parties selecting their
OL,14,Fcandidates for the contest comes as
OL,15,FMPs triggered the formal process of
OL,16,Fholding a by-election in the Labour
OL,17,FMP's vacated seat.
OL,19,FIn a process known as "moving the
OL,20,Fwrit", a by-election must now be held
OL,21,Fbetween 21 and 27 days from 19 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FIn his video, Greater Manchester Mayor
OL,7,FMr Burnham described the by-election
OL,8,Fas "the most consequential of our
OL,9,Flives" and said he did not "take
OL,10,Fanything for granted".
OL,12,FSetting out his political views, he
OL,13,Fsaid: "Manchesterism is the end of
OL,14,Fneoliberalism, the end of trickle-down
OL,15,Feconomics that has left out places
OL,16,Flike Makerfield.
OL,18,F"Make no mistake, that means a new
OL,19,Fpath for Britain."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FMr Burnham has sought to reassure
OL,7,Fvoters in the Leave-supporting
OL,8,FMakerfield constituency that he is not
OL,9,Fseeking to rejoin the European Union `
OL,10,Fsomething he said last year he would
OL,11,Flike to see happen in his lifetime.
OL,13,FAnd he has also attempted to calm the
OL,14,Fbond markets by insisting he will
OL,15,Fstick to the Government's fiscal rules.
OL,17,FReform UK has already said the
OL,18,F"expensive by-election is all about
OL,19,F(Mr Burnham's) own personal ambition"
OL,20,Frather than the best interests of the
OL,21,Fconstituency.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FThe party said the self-employed
OL,7,Fplumber, who has served as an army
OL,8,Freservist and previously worked as a
OL,9,Fspecialist technician for the NHS in
OL,10,FLancashire, will stand.
OL,12,FMr Farage said: "This by-election
OL,13,Fcontest is now a David versus Goliath
OL,14,Fbattle. This is 'the plucky plumber'
OL,15,Ftaking on 'open borders Burnham'.
OL,16,F"Only Reform UK can beat Labour in
OL,17,Fthis by-election."
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
