OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FMr Kenyon, who was born in the
OL,7,Fconstituency and won 31.8% of the vote
OL,8,Fin 2024, said: "Makerfield has never
OL,9,Fhad a member of Parliament who was
OL,10,Factually born in Makerfield.
OL,12,F"This will be a tough fight but I am
OL,13,Fgoing to give this contest my best
OL,14,Fshot."
OL,16,FThe news came as Sir Keir Starmer
OL,17,Fgathered his new-look cabinet for the
OL,18,Ffirst time since Wes Streeting
OL,19,Fresigned as Health Secretary and
OL,20,Fcalled on the Prime Minister to quit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy
OL,7,Fjoked it was "nicer week than last
OL,8,Fweek" as he arrived for the meeting,
OL,9,Fwith Sir Keir hoping to show the
OL,10,Fbusiness of government was continuing
OL,11,Fdespite the Westminster turmoil.
OL,13,FStarmer has insisted he will not set
OL,14,Fout a timetable for his departure even
OL,15,Fif the Greater Manchester mayor
OL,16,Freturns to parliament.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
