PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FIf the PM does not resign, Burnham
OL,7,Fwould need to secure the backing of 81
OL,8,FLabour MPs to mount a leadership
OL,9,Fchallenge, potentially setting up a
OL,10,Fcontest with Starmer for party
OL,11,Fmembers' votes.
OL,13,FPollster Luke Tryl, director of More
OL,14,FIn Common, said Mr Burnham's name on
OL,15,Fthe ballot paper could be worth a 20-
OL,16,Fpoint boost to Labour's prospects in a
OL,17,Fseat otherwise "tailor-made" for
OL,18,FReform UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FMr Tryl said the mayor's popularity
OL,7,Fmeant he started the race "narrowly
OL,8,Fahead", but added "anything could
OL,9,Fhappen" during the campaign, with Mr
OL,10,FBurnham's handling of a "change
OL,11,Fmessage" likely to prove vital.
OL,13,F"Andy Burnham definitely wants it to
OL,14,Fbe Andy Burnham versus Reform. If it's
OL,15,FLabour versus Reform, Reform win," he
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FAndy Burnham's four-minute campaign
OL,19,Fvideo
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
