PN,39411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FMr Burnham used a slick campaign video
OL,7,Fto set out his vision after saying his
OL,8,Fattempt to win the Makerfield by-
OL,9,Felection was motivated by the need to
OL,10,F"change Labour".
OL,12,FIn the video, soundtracked by a series
OL,13,Fof Manchester bands including Elbow,
OL,14,FJames and Oasis, Burnham said he
OL,15,Fwanted "a new path for Britain".
OL,17,FCabinet minister Pat McFadden, an ally
OL,18,Fof Sir Keir, told reporters: "Any
OL,19,Funnecessary by-election is always a
OL,20,Frisk.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]wD@HOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,F"It's the voters who have their say,
OL,7,Fbut like any by-election that is
OL,8,Fcalled for whatever reason, I want
OL,9,FLabour to win."
OL,11,FRobert Kenyon's campaign video
OL,13,FOne of Mr Burnham's supporters
OL,14,Fsuggested the mayor would not seek an
OL,15,Fimmediate leadership fight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
