OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779225068
OL,3,CReform UK and Andy Burnham to go head-
OL,4,Cto-head in by-election
OL,6,FLeeds MP Alex Sobel told LBC it was
OL,7,Fnot his "expectation" that Mr Burnham
OL,8,Fwould immediately trigger a contest,
OL,9,Fsaying he would "come back and
OL,10,Fpotentially serve in the Government,
OL,11,Ftry and help us turn this Government
OL,12,Fround".
OL,14,FMeanwhile, polling by YouGov suggested
OL,15,FMr Burnham would be Labour members'
OL,16,Fpreferred candidate for leader, with
OL,17,F47% saying he would be their first
OL,18,Fchoice for the job.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
